<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="less-and-less">less and less</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>越来越少：</strong></h4>
<p>反 more and more </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He showed less and less interest in his research. 
他对研究越来越没有兴趣了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My grandfather goes out less and less these days. 
我爷爷现在出门越来越少了。</p></div></div>